{"comments":"Sparkline Widget — Inline mini chart for trend visualization.\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nA Sparkline is a compact, inline visualization that shows data trends\nwithout axes, labels, or other chart chrome. It's designed to:\n- Fit inline with text or in table cells\n- Show trends at a glance\n- Optionally highlight min/max/last values\n- Support both line and bar variants\n\nThe widget accepts complete `SparklineData` — all points and styling\nare provided upfront. Pure data in, Element out.\n\n## Usage\n\n```purescript\nimport Hydrogen.Element.Component.Widget.Sparkline as Sparkline\n\n-- Basic sparkline\nSparkline.sparklineWidget []\n  { data: [10.0, 15.0, 12.0, 18.0, 20.0, 16.0, 22.0]\n  , color: Nothing\n  , fill: false\n  , height: Just 24\n  , width: Just 80\n  }\n\n-- With area fill\nSparkline.sparklineWidget [ Sparkline.filled true ]\n  { data: [45.0, 48.0, 51.0, 54.0]\n  , color: Just \"#10B981\"\n  , fill: true\n  , height: Nothing\n  , width: Nothing\n  }\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Render a sparkline widget.\n\nPure Element — can be rendered to DOM, Halogen, Static HTML, or any target.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":{"identifier":"msg","kind":null,"skolem":null,"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Array"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Component","Widget","Sparkline"],"SparklineProp"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Component","Widget","Sparkline"],"SparklineData"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":